OL,5, Rugby league star and motor neurone    
OL,6, disease fundraiser Rob Burrow's        
OL,7, wheelchair accessible van was          
OL,8, vandalised while his family were out   
OL,9, for a Christmas meal, his father has   
OL,10, said.                                  
OL,12,FGeoff Burrow said his son had been out 
OL,13,Fin Castleford, West Yorkshire, on      
OL,14,FFriday when the vehicle was targeted.  
OL,16,F"They made quite a lot of deep         
OL,17,Fscratches on the back of the van where 
OL,18,Fwe wheel Rob in on the ramp," he said. 
OL,20,FHe described the culprits as "cowards".
